summary: An ordinance relating to and providing for the execution of an agreement between the United States Government, Skagit County and the City of Seattle for the construction and maintenance of a bridge across the Sauk River in Section 19, Township 24 North, Range 10 East, W.M., and making an appropriation therefor and designating the construction of said bridge under the terms of said bridge under the terms of said agreement as one of the additions and betterments to and extensions of the existing Municipal Light and Power Plant and System, etc.
